{"data":[{"id":563013029,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7345c653c623ceab552193d43ace2692","url_token":"qian-zhong-chao-9","name":"钱钟超","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5a79c655f249bde5992fbe28e0745468_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5a79c655f249bde5992fbe28e0745468_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7345c653c623ceab552193d43ace2692","user_type":"people","headline":"爱我你就请我吃饭呀~","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":34,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563013029","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546172702,"updated_time":1546172702,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e关于这个问题，我想说的是，如果题主你真的是少年天才，那你早就闻名全国了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e没有一夜之间突变的天才\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e冯诺依曼六岁心算八位数除法，八岁掌握微积分，十二岁就能读懂领会《函数论》的要义。庞加莱，高斯，麦克斯韦，这些数学界物理学界的顶尖大佬，无一不是在少年时就展现出来妖怪级的超凡智力。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要想在十七八岁就做出世界级的顶尖科研成果，你得在五六岁时就展现出远超常人的突出智力，并在十多岁时就大量吸收学习该领域的顶级研究成果。唯有这样你才有可能在高考前就完成哥德巴赫猜想证明这样的成果。这样的少年天才，早就在小学初中崭露头角，被中科大少年班选为苗子重点培养了，也就不存在高考前保送清北这一说。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也有大佬成果出得晚一些，但也是深入一个领域数年数十年，皓首穷经，孜孜以求，才能百尺竿头更进一步，求得突破。这还是颇有天赋的研究者，还有无数欠缺一点天才欠缺一点灵感的研究者，穷其一生也没有做出世界级的成果，默默无闻地做着科研。而他们没有一个不是智力超群，人中龙凤，清华北大简直唾手可得。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就好像《功夫》中，包租婆说到：“除非他是万中无一的练武奇才”，酱爆跳出来比划了一通，说道：“显然我就是百年一遇的练武奇才”，被包租婆随手打翻：“显然，你不是。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主的数学天分仅仅是略高于普通人，我劝你还是好好准备高考，考个好大学找个好工作，再以数学作为自己的爱好去研究，未必不能做出点成果来。哥德巴赫本人就是个非职业的数学家，这并不影响他提出这样一个伟大的猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外，哥德巴赫猜想之所以经常成为民科的目标，而至今还没有被数学家真正证明，我觉得就在“素数”二字。素数这个东西概念非常简单，义务教育水平就能理解，但是这玩意儿研究起来难得一批，关于素数的问题动辄就是个世界级难题。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"关于这个问题，我想说的是，如果题主你真的是少年天才，那你早就闻名全国了。 \u003cb\u003e没有一夜之间突变的天才\u003c/b\u003e 冯诺依曼六岁心算八位数除法，八岁掌握微积分，十二岁就能读懂领会《函数论》的要义。庞加莱，高斯，麦克斯韦，这些数学界物理学界的顶尖大佬，无一不是…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=422\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannota